{{vgname|天天過馬路|en=Crossy Road}}是一款[[街機|街機]]風格的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]。該遊戲由安迪·孫（Andy Sum）、麥特·霍爾（Matt Hall）和班·魏瑟羅（Ben Weatherall）等人所創立的[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]公司{{tsl|en|Hipster Whale}}負責開發，並於2014年11月20日首次發行。遊戲名稱的靈感來自於常見的一則[[英文|英文]][[謎語|謎語]]：「{{tsl|en|Why did the chicken cross the road?|雞為什麼要過馬路？}}{{notetag|其謎底是「因為牠想要過到馬路的對面去」（To get to the other side.）}}」（Why did the chicken cross the road?）<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/macman/more-than-fun-and-games-with-local-developers-20150311-13usxe.html|title=More than fun and games with local developers Rylandia|date=2015-03-11|last=Barker|first=Garry|website=Digital Life|publisher={{tsl|en|Fairfax Media}}|accessdate=2015-03-22|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626110826/http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/macman/more-than-fun-and-games-with-local-developers-20150311-13usxe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《天天過馬路》曾被形容為「永無止盡的《[[青蛙過河|青蛙過河]]》」。<ref name="PolygonCR"/><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Hayward|first1=Andrew|title=You Should Play: Crossy Road is basically endless Frogger, and that's a very good thing|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2863065/you-should-play-crossy-road-is-basically-endless-frogger-and-thats-a-very-good-thing.html|website=Macworld|date=2014-12-26|access-date=2016-07-27|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819123513/https://www.macworld.com/article/2863065/you-should-play-crossy-road-is-basically-endless-frogger-and-thats-a-very-good-thing.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Rosenberg|first1=Adam|title='Crossy Road' brings a new take on its 'endless Frogger' to Apple TV|url=http://mashable.com/2015/09/09/crossy-road-apple-tv-exclusive/#cuk6W5rjnEqs|website=Mashable|date=2015-09-09|access-date=2016-07-27|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127152157/https://mashable.com/2015/09/09/crossy-road-apple-tv-exclusive/#cuk6W5rjnEqs|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 遊戲設定 ==
[[File:Crossy_Road_Gameplay.png|thumbnail]]
《天天過馬路》的遊戲目標就是盡可能在不死亡的情況下走得愈遠愈好，而中途則需跨越馬路、草地、河流和鐵軌等障礙。玩家在遊戲中可以選擇各種角色（如小雞、無尾熊或兔子等）進行遊戲，在[[觸控螢幕|觸控]]模式下若要前進則需點按一下螢幕、若需往其它方向移動則需向相應的方向滑動螢幕；在[[鍵盤|鍵盤]]模式下，則可以直接透過上下左右按鍵操控遊戲。許多障礙物會導致角色立刻死亡，例如：掉進河流中、被汽車或火車撞到等；玩家必須等待前方的道路通暢才可向前移動，或是跳躍至河流上的平台過河。若玩家停留過久或是後退超過三步，則一隻老鷹會飛來將角色叼走導致死亡。玩家每前進一步，該局就會得到一分，而每達到50步時，遊戲會發出一個特殊音效。此外，玩家可以在遊戲進行中撿拾不時出現在地圖中的金幣；每收集滿100枚金幣，玩家即可至遊戲內的[[轉蛋|轉蛋機]]抽新的角色。<ref name="toucharcadeCR">{{en}}{{cite web|url = http://toucharcade.com/2014/11/21/crossy-road-review/|title = Crossy Road" Review - Watch Out for That Train!|publisher = TouchArcade|date = 2014-11-21|last = Dotson|first = Carter|access-date = 2016-07-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170502144035/http://toucharcade.com/2014/11/21/crossy-road-review/|archive-date = 2017-05-02|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

===角色===
[[iOS|iOS]]版本中的《天天過馬路》共包含145個角色可供遊玩，而預設的角色是一隻[[鸡|小鸡]]。其中，有119個是可透過收集金幣後至轉蛋機取得的角色，其餘的22個則是「隱藏角色」，必須利用特定的角色在遊戲進行中完成特殊任務才可獲得；[[扑满|貪吃豬]]、[[PSY|PSY]]和[[吃豆人|PAC-MAN]]等角色則只能透過遊戲內購（in-app purchase）取得。除此之外，[[Android|Android]]版本中還有額外角色安卓（Android Robot），其外觀近似該[[行動作業系統|行動作業系統]]的商標。其它角色還包括[[绿头鸭|绿头鸭]]、[[草泥马|草泥马]]、[[阿奇·安德鲁|Archie]]、[[Doge|多吉]]、[[Windows_3.x|3.1]]、[[The_dress|#thedress]]、[[韓式泡菜|泡菜]]、[[韓國烤肉|韓國烤肉]]和來自《[[纪念碑谷_(游戏)|紀念碑谷]]》的公主艾達和图腾等等。

===金幣===
金幣是遊戲中的貨幣，其唯一用途就是在[[轉蛋|轉蛋機]]中使用；每次轉蛋需要100枚金幣<ref name="toucharcadeCR" />，可能隨機獲得新的角色或是已經擁有的重覆角色。玩家除了可以在遊戲進行中撿拾外，也可以透過觀看廣告影片、完成任務獲得金幣；此外，玩家每隔數小時也可領取一份免費金幣禮物，其數量介於數十至數百枚之間；或是利用真實世界的貨幣購買遊戲中的金幣。玩家目前所擁有的金幣數量則會在遊戲畫面的右上角顯示。

當玩家擁有貪吃豬角色後，遊戲中就會出現可撿拾的紅色金幣，每獲得一枚紅色金幣相當於五枚普通的金幣；此外，玩家觀看廣告影片或是領取免費禮物所獲得的金幣數量也會加倍。

==開發==
最初，遊戲的製作團隊計畫在六週的時間內完成《天天過馬路》的開發，但在發現這款遊戲的潛力後決定額外再增加六週的開發時間。<ref name="Lifehacker">{{en}}{{cite web|last1 = Kidman|first1 = Angus|title = Why Crossy Road's Developers Launched On Android Through Amazon|url = http://www.lifehacker.com.au/2014/12/why-crossy-roads-developers-launched-on-android-through-amazon/|website = Lifehacker Australia|accessdate = 2014-12-27|date = 2014-12-18|archive-date = 2020-08-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200808185409/https://www.lifehacker.com.au/2014/12/why-crossy-roads-developers-launched-on-android-through-amazon/|dead-url = no}}</ref>開發人員麥特·霍爾（Matt Hall）表示，《天天過馬路》的設計靈感來自《[[青蛙過河|青蛙過河]]》、《[[神廟逃亡|神廟逃亡]]》、《[[地鐵跑酷|地鐵跑酷]]》、《{{tsl|en|Disco Zoo}}》、《[[Flappy_Bird|Flappy Bird]]》、《[[Skylanders|Skylanders]]》、《{{tsl|en|Tiny Wings}}》和《[[菲斯_(遊戲)|菲斯]]》等遊戲<ref name="MaHaTw">{{en}}{{cite web|url = https://twitter.com/KlickTock/status/538471575838674945|title = Matt Hall (@KlickTock) on Twitter|publisher = [[Twitter|Twitter]]|date = 2014-11-28|last = Hall|first = Matt|access-date = 2016-07-27|archive-date = 2016-04-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160421091819/https://twitter.com/klicktock/status/538471575838674945|dead-url = no}}</ref>，而遊戲[[网络游戏免费模式|免费模式]]的模型是參考自《[[Dota_2|Dota 2]]》。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{en}}{{cite web|last1 = Te|first1 = Zorine|title = Crossy Road's Surprising Success, Future Secrets, Dota 2 Connection|url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/crossy-road-s-surprising-success-future-secrets-do/1100-6424376/|website = Gamespot|accessdate = 2014-12-27|date = 2014-12-24|archive-date = 2020-11-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111173333/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/crossy-road-s-surprising-success-future-secrets-do/1100-6424376/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==反響==
《天天過馬路》在評論界中受到了廣泛的好評。遊戲在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上的得分為88/100<ref name="MetacriticCR">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/crossy-road---endless-arcade-hopper|title=Crossy Road - Endless Arcade Hopper iOS|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|access-date=2016-07-27|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207081718/https://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/crossy-road---endless-arcade-hopper|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[手机游戏|手機遊戲]]評論網站[[TouchArcade|TouchArcade]]和BigBoomBoom.com都給了它5/5顆星<ref name="toucharcadeCR" /><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.bigboomboom.com/reviews/crossy-road-iphone-android-game-review |title=Crossy Road iPhone and Android Game Review |date=2015-01-20 |website=Big Boom Boom |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120232850/http://www.bigboomboom.com/reviews/crossy-road-iphone-android-game-review |archivedate=2015-01-20 |access-date=2016-07-27 }}</ref>、[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo Gaming]]給了它4.5/5顆星<ref name="GamezeboGamingCR">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezebo.com/2014/11/20/crossy-road-review/|title=Crossy Road Review: Traffic's a Zoo|date=2014-11-20|last=Cymet|first=Eli|publisher=[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo Gaming]]|access-date=2016-07-27|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130085240/https://www.gamezebo.com/2014/11/20/crossy-road-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、Apple N' Apps則給了它4/5顆星。<ref name="ApplenAppsCR">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://applenapps.com/review/crossy-roads-enjoying-crossing-side#.VHHV34vF8kw|title=Crossy Road – Enjoying Crossing To The Other Side|date=2014-11-20|last=Sheridan|first=Trevor|publisher=Apple N' Apps|access-date=2016-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731111832/http://applenapps.com/review/crossy-roads-enjoying-crossing-side#.VHHV34vF8kw|archive-date=2017-07-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]稱遊戲「非常優秀」（brilliant），並將其比喻為一款升級版的《[[青蛙過河|青蛙過河]]》<ref name="PolygonCR">{{en}}{{cite web|url = http://www.polygon.com/2014/11/21/7260459/crossy-road-frogger|title = Crossy Road has invented the 'endless Frogger,' and it's brilliant|publisher = [[Polygon|Polygon]]|date = 2014-11-21|last = Kuchera|first = Ben|access-date = 2016-07-27|archive-date = 2019-11-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191128232703/https://www.polygon.com/2014/11/21/7260459/crossy-road-frogger|dead-url = no}}</ref>；《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》則認為遊戲「結合了《青蛙過河》和《[[Flappy_Bird|Flappy Bird]]》」。<ref name="TIMECR">{{en}}{{cite web|url = https://time.com/3602328/crossy-road-iphone/|title = Crossy Road Is Your New iPhone Game Addiction|work = [[時代_(雜誌)|TIME]]|date = 2014-11-24|last = Fitzpatrick|first = Alex|access-date = 2016-07-27|archive-date = 2017-05-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170520102202/http://time.com/3602328/crossy-road-iphone/|dead-url = no}}</ref>遊戲發行後於2014年的澳大利亞遊戲開發者獎項（Australian Game Developer Awards）中進入決賽，並成為該獎項「2014年度最佳遊戲」的前五名之一。<ref name="GCAP14">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://gcap.com.au/australian-game-developer-awards-finalists-announced/ |title=Australian Game Developer Awards Finalists Announced |date=2014-10-15 |publisher=GCAP |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228065843/http://gcap.com.au/australian-game-developer-awards-finalists-announced/ |archivedate=2015-02-28 |deadurl=yes |access-date=2016-07-27 }}</ref>後來，《天天過馬路》又在2015年的[[蘋果全球開發者大會|蘋果全球開發者大會]]上獲得了2015年度的[[蘋果設計獎|蘋果設計獎]]。<ref name="WWDC">{{en}}{{cite web|url = http://www.cnet.com/au/news/crossy-road-vainglory-take-apple-design-awards/|title = Crossy Road, Vainglory take Apple Design Awards|publisher = [[CNET|CNET]]|date = 2015-06-09|last = Starr|first = Michelle|access-date = 2016-07-27|archive-date = 2018-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180924145632/https://www.cnet.com/au/news/crossy-road-vainglory-take-apple-design-awards/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

在遊戲發行之後三個月，《天天過馬路》獲得了約1000萬美元的收入，並有約5000萬的下載次數。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/3/3/8142247/crossy-road-earnings-10-million-gdc-2015|title=They wanted to make a video game phenomenon. They made $10 million. The story of Crossy Road.|last=Tach|first=Dave|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=Vox Media|date=2015-03-08|accessdate=2015-09-05|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212100915/https://www.polygon.com/2015/3/3/8142247/crossy-road-earnings-10-million-gdc-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==《迪士尼天天過馬路》==
2016年，{{Tsl|en|Hipster Whale}}和{{Tsl|en|Disney Interactive Studios|迪士尼互动工作室}}合作發行了《天天過馬路》的[[番外|番外]]作品——《迪士尼天天過馬路》，適用的平台包括[[iOS|iOS]]、[[Android|Android]]、[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]等。遊戲的玩法和原作幾乎完全相同，不過玩家可以選擇[[华特迪士尼公司|迪士尼]]的卡通角色進行遊戲，包括[[米老鼠|米老鼠]]和[[唐老鸭|唐老鸭]]等。除此之外，遊戲還包含了來自數個迪士尼及[[皮克斯动画工作室|皮克斯]]電影中的角色，如《[[狮子王|狮子王]]》、《[[魔髮奇緣|魔髮奇緣]]》、《[[无敌破坏王|无敌破坏王]]》、《[[玩具总动员|玩具总动员]]》和《[[腦筋急轉彎_(電影)|腦筋急轉彎]]》等。遊戲中共有超過600個角色，其中也有部分是需透過特殊任務才可取得的隱藏角色。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Farokhmanesh|first1=Megan|title=Disney Crossy Road launches today for mobile devices|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/4/7/11380924/disney-crossy-release-date-mobile|website=Polygon|accessdate=2016-04-12|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112025/http://www.polygon.com/2016/4/7/11380924/disney-crossy-release-date-mobile|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，《迪士尼天天過馬路》包含了一些原作沒有的功能——像是玩家可以完成每日任務（如跳達一定步數或嚇跑小鳥等）以取得新的隱藏角色。

